Have you visited Bombay Brow lately? 

If not, then we invite you to take advantage of your 2-1 brow service offer at Bombay Waterfront. Book any brow service and receive a bonus service on us. Use code WFSHARELOVE at our online check-out or book over the phone.

Our team of trained beauticians can help you: 

✔️ get those brows under control
✔️ minimize pores and slough off dead skin 
✔️ relax with our marma facial massage

Stop in and enjoy a relaxing spa experience, and leave feeling refreshed.

So stop by our Waterfront location at 829 Cordova Street in Vancouver. We're only THREE minutes from the Waterfront train station.

Book by clicking the link in our bio and type in “WFSHARELOVE” in the promo code box to schedule your appointment.
